    "name": "Jack of Clubs Golf",
    "steam_appid": 3057820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jack of Clubs is a 2D golf game where hitting the ball is only half the battle! You play as Jack, a pilot stranded on a recently abandoned golf utopia. As you traverse the course in pursuit of your ball, you'll explore the resort, fight off robots, uncover secrets, and help the locals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and climb your way through two huge nine-hole maps in this hybrid of golf and action-adventure. The course is full of secrets to discover and challenges to complete in exchange for consumable items that improve your golf game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057820/extras/d8b9670758c21484e1fdc6a720659137.poster.avif?t=1762193909\" width=800 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057820/extras/d8b9670758c21484e1fdc6a720659137.webm?t=1762193909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057820/extras/d8b9670758c21484e1fdc6a720659137.mp4?t=1762193909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main story takes roughly four hours to complete, but the fun doesn't end there! Add hours of gameplay by completing more than 140 &quot;safaris&quot;. Want to hit the ball from from tee #3 into hole #7? Do it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack by DJ Beatza Hut, Roderic Russell, and Nick Powell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alongside your Steam friends! In <strong>online multiplayer</strong>, a &quot;ghost&quot; of each player and their ball appears after every stroke. When a player completes a hole, other players get a notification. Up to 32 players.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057820/extras/e09e735641508a2f0930a99a7316c982.avif?t=1762193909\" width=1560 height=855 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Three game modes</strong>: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mode is the original Jack of Clubs experience. You take no damage, but robots can hit you and prevent you from golfing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Friendly mode pacifies the robots for those who want a pure golf experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard mode adds a three-heart life meter, and a stroke is added to your score if it gets to zero. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller and mouse and keyboard support with rebindable inputs. Lots of achievements. Family friendly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*In theory. I don't have enough friends to test a full 32-player lobby.</i></p>",
